name: Dotted Scatter Pattern #001
description:
Coding was a charm for me too. I was satisfied every time I spent time on it. So after a few days of effort, I was able to find good coding. I was able to find a lot of different arts from that. In hindsight, I realized that this was not something that could be done so easily. This is done by adjusting each point at angles X, Y, and Z over time.



This takes us to another level of vision. Helps to forget some stressors. It does not make the mind think of anything else. I felt very calm. So it seemed to me that this art could provide something else. So I think it's worth it.
